_____________________
The choices package
v0.1

This package adjusts the choices of the multiple choice question automatically.

It is wholly inspired by the work of Enrico Gregorio
and improved by Vafa Khalighi and I am just packed it and
redistribute it under the name of `choices` package.

Current version release date: 2022/06/24
